// The enabled-mods list: each entry is a mod bundle manifest path, relative to
// the asset root, loaded AFTER the base and overlaid by id (a mod overrides the
// base). Ships EMPTY so the base game is pristine. To try the bundled demo mod,
// add its bundle path:
//
//   (mods: ["mods/demo/demo.bundle.ron"])
//
// See assets/mods/demo/README.md.
(mods: [])
